  "keyFeatures": [
    "12-module structured learning path from fundamentals to production-ready MCP implementations",
    "Cross-language code examples in C#, Java, TypeScript, JavaScript, Rust, and Python",
    "Hands-on labs covering MCP server architecture, security, PostgreSQL integration, and Azure deployment",
    "Security-first curriculum covering OAuth2, Entra ID authentication, and MCP-specific security best practices",
    "Real-world integrations with VS Code, Claude Desktop, Azure AI Foundry, and other MCP hosts",
    "13-lab capstone module for building production MCP servers with database integration",
    "Multi-language support with automated translations in 48+ languages",
    "Coverage of advanced topics: real-time streaming, semantic search, multi-modality, and context engineering"
  ],
